自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"711132718e0792b8e928ce5f62761fffd90acaae","tid":1558791,"uid":168444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356c9138110e45034f26a59b1b507e218e832de5","tid":1558791,"uid":30528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5471be0f4ae7054f657758f1a395175f63ed5746","tid":1558791,"uid":168444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"想知唔相同多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"我有兩個friend係藍黃配，有一對個黃成日鬧藍，個藍係愛錢不愛國嗰種，一齊左五年。每次鬧完交都冇事。<br />\n<br />\n另一對係禁止講政治，一齊左半年。一鬧完交就真係好似會分手個種，所以先唔可以傾政治。我心諗，半年呢pair不如散左佢算。<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人係黃黃配。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"拍拖最多咪分手，最慘係結咗婚先知唔同政見"},{"pid":"a1d88017dddf43f9462d2f12db56d3b53dec7d9e","tid":1558791,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"我哋要繼續開展社區戰線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sBTyU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sBTyU4.jpg&h=de779003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨身帶備歌詞派/airdrop俾途人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要入屋!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440d86bb4345395e8a7d8862ed3653bb13fa5f4f","tid":1558791,"uid":30528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"711132718e0792b8e928ce5f62761fffd90acaae","tid":1558791,"uid":168444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356c9138110e45034f26a59b1b507e218e832de5","tid":1558791,"uid":30528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{